<div id="descriptionContainer">
  
      <div id="description" class="readable stacked" style="right:0">
        
<span id="freeTextContainer11970921907241369687">It&apos;s the twenty-fifth century, and advances in technology have redefined life itself. A person&apos;s consciousness can now be stored in the brain and downloaded into a new body (or &quot;sleeve&quot;), making death nothing more than a minor blip on a screen. Onetime U.N. Envoy Takeshi Kovacs has been killed before, but his last death was particularly painful. Resleeved into a body in Ba</span>
  <span id="freeText11970921907241369687" style="display:none">It's the twenty-fifth century, and advances in technology have redefined life itself. A person's consciousness can now be stored in the brain and downloaded into a new body (or "sleeve"), making death nothing more than a minor blip on a screen. Onetime U.N. Envoy Takeshi Kovacs has been killed before, but his last death was particularly painful. Resleeved into a body in Bay City (formerly San Francisco), Kovacs is thrown into the dark heart of a shady, far-reaching conspiracy that is vicious even by the standards of a society that treats existence as something that can be bought and sold. For Kovacs, the shell that blew a hole in his chest was only the beginning.<br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="11970921907241369687" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

